### Scientific conclusion (statistical)
Band-count effects are measurable and reproducible under deterministic null tests; n=37 may be locally competitive depending on metric, but not universally dominant across all criteria. Subdomain analyses indicate heterogeneous stability, with stronger separation in some periodic slices and weaker separation in others. Reported conclusions are statistical only and do not imply mechanism.
